    shortAnswer: `A CHAMP qualification template gives you ready questions for the four elements: Challenges, Authority, Money, and Prioritization. Lead with challenges to build trust, then work through authority, funding, and where this ranks against the buyer's other priorities. Paste the questions below into your call notes or CRM.`,
