    rookRuns: `the real pain is captured on every deal`,
    shortAnswer: `Uncover pain in discovery by moving past the surface request to the root cause and its consequences. Ask what is not working, why it happens, what has been tried, and what it leads to downstream. The goal is to find the compelling reason to act, because a deal without real, felt pain rarely closes.`,
