    shortAnswer: `Configure quote approval workflows by setting discount thresholds that trigger different approval levels, routing each quote automatically to the right approver, and keeping approval turnaround fast with clear SLAs. Good approval workflows protect margin on the deals that need oversight while letting reps quote freely within their guardrails.`,
