    kw: `negotiation techniques, leverage, close on value`,
    desc: `Sales negotiation tactics that protect margin: anchor, trade concessions, use silence, and never negotiate against yourself. Practical techniques inside.`,
    rookRuns: `reps negotiate from a planned position`,
    shortAnswer: `Effective sales negotiation tactics include anchoring first when you have information, trading every concession for a give-get, using silence to transfer pressure, isolating objections before responding, and never negotiating against yourself. The goal is a deal both sides value, reached by trading rather than caving, and grounded in the quantified value you established earlier.`,
