    shortAnswer: `A pipeline review agenda template structures a focused 30-minute meeting: a quick metrics check, deals that moved, stuck deals to unstick, the largest deals in the period, and committed next steps. It keeps the review from becoming a deal-by-deal narration and ensures every meeting drives action. Copy the agenda below.`,
