    shortAnswer: `Develop sales reps by assessing their skills and aspirations, building a growth path that connects the job to a career, coaching continuously on the highest-impact gaps, and stretching them with new challenges and responsibilities. Development retains your best people and builds your future leaders, and it is one of the strongest levers a manager has for both performance and retention.`,
