    shortAnswer: `A sales comp plan checklist covers the essentials of a plan that motivates the right behavior: it is simple enough to calculate, aligned to the outcomes you want, offers uncapped upside, includes accelerators for overperformance, and is stable and fair. Score your plan against it to catch the design flaws that drive unintended behavior. Copy the checklist below.`,
