    shortAnswer: `Prioritize your pipeline by concentrating time on the deals that are both most likely to close and most valuable, honestly disqualifying deals that will not close, and resisting the pull of comfortable but weak deals. A rep's time is the scarce resource, so directing it toward the highest-probability, highest-value deals is one of the biggest levers on their number.`,
